com.stripe.android.model

Class PaymentMethod

  • com.stripe.android.model.PaymentMethod
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StripeModel

    public class PaymentMethod
implements StripeModel

    PaymentMethod objects represent your customer's payment instruments. They can be used with PaymentIntents to collect payments or saved to Customer objects to store instrument details for future payments.

    Related guides: Payment Methods and More Payment Scenarios.

    See class PaymentMethodCreateParams for PaymentMethod creation

    See Also:
    PaymentMethod, PaymentIntents, Payment Methods, More Payment Scenarios, class PaymentMethodCreateParams
